title: Problem BaronReplay
body:
Hey,
Im Phnex and have a Problem with BaronReplay.
I rly dont know if im in the right section or somenthing but i rly need some help with this.
I use BaronReplay to record my Games and have a little YT Channel with an friend. My Problem now is, that i have some stuff i want to Record from previous Version (5.19). I Loaded that Version (5.19), put BaronReplay as Rule in my Firewall as IN and Outgoing Rule but i get the Error : "Unable to download spectator data. The game will now Exit". I can Replay from versions under and over 5.19. So i dont UNderstand why this happens. I can Replay 5.18, 5.20, 5.21 and 5.22. I dont know what elso to do.
Does someone have a Clue or had the same issue and fixed it? Please let me know.

Best Regards

Phinex
